(287830, 9468, 287715, '12GAUGE', 608, '', 1344585436, 'Great looking target however there are few things of concern here:\r\n\r\n1. if we make it too heavy, it might not roll at all\r\n2. if we make it too light, we might run the risk of permanently damaging the steel plates\r\n3. we also need to estimate the length of rods (tentacles) as a longer length will prevent it from rolling and a shorter length will roll out of control.\r\n\r\nother than that, its a pretty simple and do-able idea.\r\n\r\nRegards.', 1, 1, '39.47.224.179', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
