s of experience as junior clerk.. (While studying law was already working with a lawyer, learning tricks of trade). Any ways.. if i can be of any help i will surely do so.[/QUOTE]\n\n\n@ Atiq \nSection 99 and 103 of PPC  \nMay contradict with your first paragraph\n\nAnd No hard feelings ma bro :-)', 1, 0, '39.47.245.209', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
